OL,3,CAndy Burnham brings promise to end
OL,4,Crough sleeping to Westminster
OL,6,FThe new prime minister has said his
OL,7,Ffirst instruction to his Government as
OL,8,Fprime minister will be to "end rough
OL,9,Fsleeping in our country".
OL,11,FUnder his mayorship, Greater
OL,12,FManchester ran "A Bed Every Night"
OL,13,Fprogramme ` to which Andy Burnham
OL,14,Fpledged to donate at least 15% of his
OL,15,Fsalary ` to help bring rough sleepers
OL,16,Fin off the streets.
OL,18,FBut official figures published in 2025
OL,19,Fby the Greater Manchester Combined
OL,20,FAuthority showed that rough sleeping
OL,21,Frose during his time as the Mayor.
OL,26,@tD@POUtD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
