PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784737124
OL,3,CAndy Burnham brings promise to end
OL,4,Crough sleeping to Westminster
OL,6,FMr Burnham previously claimed some of
OL,7,Fthe blame for the increase lied with
OL,8,Fthe Labour Government's Home Office.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV News in December 2025,
OL,11,Fhe said: "I'm going to be honest and
OL,12,Fsay the task that we have faced has
OL,13,Fnot been made easier by the actions of
OL,14,Fthe Home Office in recent times...
OL,15,Fevicting people with short notice who
OL,16,Fhaven't got anywhere to go.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784737124
OL,3,CAndy Burnham brings promise to end
OL,4,Crough sleeping to Westminster
OL,6,F"I look back at my old workplace
OL,7,FWestminster and they pose as being
OL,8,Ftough on benefits... but what I've
OL,9,Fseen (as Mayor) is that when these
OL,10,Fdecisions are taken it just builds the
OL,11,Fnumber of families presenting as
OL,12,Fhomeless."
OL,14,FBut now that the buck stops with Mr
OL,15,FBurnham, the new prime minster has
OL,16,Fvowed to make ending homelessness a
OL,17,Fpriority for his Government.
OL,26,@qD@FpmqD@Opn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
