OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784737124
OL,3,CAndy Burnham brings promise to end
OL,4,Crough sleeping to Westminster
OL,6,FJust hours before formally becoming
OL,7,Fthe UK's new leader, he visited
OL,8,Fhomelessness charity The Passage in
OL,9,FVictoria, London.
OL,11,FMr Burnham said his early morning
OL,12,Fvisit was the "best place to start"
OL,13,Fahead of his premiership, visiting
OL,14,Fsuch a charity to see "the lives that
OL,15,Fare being turned around".
OL,26,@tD@OOUtD@cO]vD@WOUwD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
