CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784737124
OL,3,CAndy Burnham brings promise to end
OL,4,Crough sleeping to Westminster
OL,6,FSpeaking in Downing Street, in his
OL,7,Ffirst speech as PM, he told gathered
OL,8,Fsupporters and journalists: "I will
OL,9,Fsoon go through that door behind me
OL,10,Fand issue my first instruction: to end
OL,11,Frough sleeping in our country."
OL,13,FThe number of people seen sleeping
OL,14,Frough on a single night in Greater
OL,15,FManchester rose by 3.4% to 154 in
OL,16,Fautumn 2024 from 149 in 2023.
OL,18,FThe authority said this was still
OL,19,Fbelow the 268 at the peak in 2017.
OL,26,@pD@]OUsD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784737124
OL,3,CAndy Burnham brings promise to end
OL,4,Crough sleeping to Westminster
OL,6,FPressed on the rise, during an
OL,7,Finterview at The Passage on Monday, 20
OL,8,FJuly, Mr Burnham suggested support is
OL,9,Fneeded across the board to make a
OL,10,Fdifference.
OL,12,FHe referred to the "Everyone In"
OL,13,Fscheme during the Covid-19 pandemic,
OL,14,Fwhen thousands of rough sleepers
OL,15,Facross England were taken in off the
OL,16,Fstreets.
OL,18,FHe said: "What I learned was, we ran a
OL,19,Fscheme every night, 600 beds, called A
OL,20,FBed Every Night and we funded it
OL,21,Fthrough various different ways.
OL,26,@tD@TOUtD@`O]zD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784737124
OL,3,CAndy Burnham brings promise to end
OL,4,Crough sleeping to Westminster
OL,6,F"But we were the only place that was
OL,7,Fdoing it and you won't be able to get
OL,8,Fthe numbers down if you're the only
OL,9,Fplace, and other cities, people are
OL,10,Fcoming to Manchester.
OL,12,F"So it taught me that the only way is
OL,13,Fto do this together. Everybody pulling
OL,14,Fin the same direction, Everyone In, as
OL,15,Fwe did in the pandemic ` because we
OL,16,Fdid bring people inside in the
OL,17,Fpandemic and that's what I'm saying as
OL,18,FI go into Government today.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784737124
OL,3,CAndy Burnham brings promise to end
OL,4,Crough sleeping to Westminster
OL,6,F"We did it then. We can do it now. Get
OL,7,Fthe basics right. Put a care for
OL,8,Fpeople at the heart of everything that
OL,9,Fwe do and just get this country
OL,10,Fworking as it should again."
OL,12,FHe described The Passage as "an
OL,13,Famazing shelter that supports people
OL,14,Fwho are street homeless, people
OL,15,Frecovering from homelessness".
OL,17,FHe added: "It was the best place to
OL,18,Fstart, to see what is being done here,
OL,19,Fthe lives that are being turned
OL,20,Faround."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@\O]tD@]OUwD@]O]yD@KOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
