PN,36909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784737124
OL,3,CAndy Burnham brings promise to end
OL,4,Crough sleeping to Westminster
OL,6,FAfter accompanying charity workers out
OL,7,Fon the streets on their daily check-in
OL,8,Fwith rough sleepers in the Victoria
OL,9,Farea, Mr Burnham returned to The
OL,10,FPassage building to help with food
OL,11,Fpreparation by chopping mushrooms for
OL,12,Fthe day's breakfast and lunch.
OL,14,FHe told the charity's Chief Executive,
OL,15,FMick Clarke, that he had "seen your
OL,16,Fworld from the ground" as Greater
OL,17,FManchester Mayor.
OL,26,@wD@ZOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
