OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784737124
OL,3,CAndy Burnham brings promise to end
OL,4,Crough sleeping to Westminster
OL,6,FHe said: "When you have that
OL,7,Fexperience, you can do something with
OL,8,Fit when you are back at the national
OL,9,Flevel. You change lives everyday
OL,10,F(here)."
OL,12,FThe latest annual national statistics,
OL,13,Fpublished by the Government in
OL,14,FFebruary 2026, estimated there were
OL,15,F4,793 people sleeping rough on a
OL,16,Fsingle night in autumn 2025 in England.
OL,18,FThis was a new record high and the
OL,19,Ffourth annual increase in a row.
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
